eve_daemon - rough pseudocode for eve functionality

get timestamp of bpf.py and bpf.c
if timestamp is newer
    send SIGINT to $PROCESS
    PROCESS = python bpf.py
    slow serial blink to indicate that modification function was updated:
    serial.light1.blink1()

if interface1.isUp() and interface2.isUp()
    serial.light2.on()
else
    serial.light2.blink()
